metadata.symbol: The Robbie Fowler digital memorabilia experience
metadata.description:
Inspired by Liverpool’s landmark Royal Liverbuilding, synonymous with both Liverpool and Robbie. 

‘God’ is the collection’s unique and exclusive 1 of 1 piece that is reserved for the auction’s lucky winning bidder. 

In addition to the NFT, the winning bidder will receive:

  • a signed Robbie Fowler jersey
  • a signed pair of match-worn football boots
  • a signed copy of Robbie’s autobiography
  • a signed print version of the NFT
  • a video call with Robbie
  • and two tickets accompanied by Robbie himself to a Liverpool home game for 2021/22 season.
metadata.title: “God”
metadata.subtitle: The ultimate fan experience with Robbie
